#

Pumpkin Seed Soup

30 min
$7.5
250 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

Nuts

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianGluten-Free

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Main Dish

Tags:

SoupComfort FoodEasy

Description

A creamy and nutty soup that warms the soul, perfect for fall evenings.

Ingredients

  • pumpkin seeds: 1 cup
  • vegetable broth: 4 cups
  • onion: 1, chopped
  • garlic: 2 cloves, minced
  • olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • cumin: 1 teaspoon
  • salt: to taste
  • pepper: to taste
  • heavy cream or coconut milk (optional): 1/2 cup
